node.text:
After moving from strongman to boxing it was important for me to consider the stack of supplements I was using.  My training has changed a lot so I turned to @transparentlabs lineup to keep me fuelled as effectively as they did during my World Record Deadlift training.   @transparentlabs has launched both The Mountain Pack and World’s Strongest Stack on www.transparentlabs.com/hafthor  Use the Code: THOR72 to save 20% for the next 72hours  To learn more about the World’s Strongest Stack head over to @transparentlabs where I take you through both of my stacks 

  #transparentlabs #TLmakingitcount 
#worldsstrongeststack #mountainpack
#supplements

node.title: Check out a Full Day with The Mountain Pack from @transparentlabs .

node.text: Most of you know I tested positive for covid-19 last week. I’ve been feeling much better so I wanted to see how many push-ups I could do in a row. I know they weren’t the perfect push-ups but I’m pretty happy with the outcome considering having covid, my current body weight and lack of exercise the last week. How many can you do?

node.title: How many push-ups can I do?

node.text:
#AssassinsCreedValhalla is coming out on November 10th, and for the occasion @Ubisoft created the first remote race of longships. Some players around the world were invited to show their viking energy in the most epic challenge: The Viking Crossing. They challenged each other for a chance to face me! 
Check out the video
Now, it’s your turn to build your own Viking legend on #assassinscreedvalhalla #likeaviking

node.title: Assassins Creed Valhalla is coming out on November 10th. @ubisoft

Triceps extensions 15 reps 4 sets

Try this at home. This workout is a killer! 🤯 @kelc33
